                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080914-41-off233 t18080914-41-crimeloc235"></join>. On the 18th of July, about ten minutes after six in the morning, I left all the articles mentioned in the indictment in my room; the prisoner lodged in my house. About a quarter before eight I returned; my property was gone, and the prisoner was gone: I left nobody in the house but her and my two children; one is four years old and the other is six years old. I intrusted her in the same house, she worked in the same manufactory as me.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you desire her to take care of the children in your absence - A. I called her up to go to her work - she never has been to the manufactory since.</p>
               <p>Q. Is 
               <persName id="t18080914-41-person380">
